article_title: WHO chief announces death of colleague in Gaza.
sentence: Last  night,  the  World  Health  Organization  (WHO)  chief  said  one  of  its  employees  -  Dima  Alhaj  -  had  been  killed  in  Gaza,  along  with  her  six-month-old  baby,  husband  and  two  brothers.

article_title: WHO chief announces death of colleague in Gaza.
sentence: He  said  108  UN  workers  had  been  killed  in  Gaza  since  7  October.
